# Build context hygiene for apps/worker-node/Dockerfile.
# The worker image rebuilds node_modules/dist from the lockfile + source, so
# never ship host artifacts into the build context (smaller, reproducible).
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/coverage
**/.next
**/__pycache__
**/*.egg-info
**/.pytest_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/.venv
**/.coverage
**/.turbo
.git
samples
vendor
design-explorations
*.png
